                <li>Articles written, optimised, and published live</li>
                <li>Human editorial QA before every push</li>
                <li>Auto-publishes to WordPress / Webflow / Ghost</li>
                <li>Bundle with GBP + social at $167/mo all-in</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
