                <li>Not for one-off articles, built for cadence</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Operators that want ranked articles, not drafts to finish.</div>
            <a href="/checkout/" class="tool-cta-btn">Start at $99/mo →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
